Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:28.54,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願っても何もできないと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}わかってはいるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:33.13,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}失う怖さが邪魔をしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:35.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}誰しも明日へ向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:37.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}見えない 知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:40.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}自由も愛も与えて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:44.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}さぁ選べ  舞い降りた天使達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:47.27,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}感じる予感に Shoot the arrow of fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:51.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}翼に意志を 身を委ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:54.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}倦まず弛まず
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}ただ 生きてたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:58.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}もう いっそ嘘でもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:01.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}正義を貫く 最後で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:04.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}「幸せになりたい」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:12.71,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}ただそれだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}It ain’t over till it’s over(Shoot!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:21.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}勇往邁進 GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:28.54,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}即使祈愿 也什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.42,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}明明知道如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:33.13,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}哪怕失去的恐惧作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:35.59,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}人们还是会走向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:37.76,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}看不见 不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:40.22,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}给他自由与爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:44.35,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}好了 选择吧 飞舞降临的天使们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:47.27,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}向察觉的预感 射出命运之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:51.77,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}灌注意志于翅膀  委身于它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:54.02,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}不知疲倦 从不松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.36,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}只是 想要活着而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:58.99,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}不管了 就算撒谎也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:01.28,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}贯穿正义 到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:04.20,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}说一句「我想要幸福」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:12.71,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.96,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}它不会结束 直到它结束 (发射!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:21.76,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}勇往直前 GO!
